{"tid":106670,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人去過森林餐廳？","createTime":"2017-02-03T22:17:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-10T00:05:02.000Z","uid":8175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1367712e787c2f1a47e010128d63c6079581ecb8","tid":106670,"uid":8175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T22:17:49.000Z","msg":"究竟入面係點？野食好唔好味？<br />\n<br />\n細個屋企冇錢入唔到去食，次次經過都淨係喺門口望住隻長頸鹿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f45fb0f1ed5ad90eae7c81ce182656116f0b63e6","tid":106670,"uid":67617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T22:29:12.000Z","msg":"十幾年前細個去過一次 <br />\n好記得比啲動物叫聲嚇到喊晒口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n環境又黑 細個覺得超恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n啲野好唔好食就唔記得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94a22b785d3a8f1c1874c52d4c88e077e4212be6","tid":106670,"uid":2155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T00:56:45.000Z","msg":"之前無咪有間超人餐廳"},{"pid":"44a18e24e978857554dffdfecb28b3f7c09d9ee6","tid":106670,"uid":17174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T01:53:09.000Z","msg":"垃圾 又貴又唔好食 連個仔都唔想去第二次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 嘈住話要食麥記 之後間野好快執左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5156a6316122256df551fd1423403b37b167beb8","tid":106670,"uid":44289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T02:15:47.000Z","msg":"嘢食太細個唔記得喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我淨係記得果時覺得水池條鱷魚好迫真，同埋棵大樹都好得人驚吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bbf9f270c1d4a8fc02e5008fc24832b4e99f22c","tid":106670,"uid":42009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T02:33:12.000Z","msg":"之前又一城個間？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e372f188ec1c90be71025e8e548d21b9f042efb","tid":106670,"uid":8893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T03:54:09.000Z","msg":"入面好恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n童年陰影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03975f6207054ac655a7fdcf2b549158b9b77987","tid":106670,"uid":8175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T07:08:11.000Z","msg":"入面究竟係點 點解你地講到咁恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e738288f2d247e1fe918bb18aa02d6aa59e86d0","tid":106670,"uid":73671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T14:57:45.000Z","msg":"又一城果間，我細個成日去"},{"pid":"78857f4f3680bfb2e42bf69245f6fc3e1eece33f","tid":106670,"uid":7248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T15:33:18.000Z","msg":"已經唔太記得d食物"},{"pid":"f79bd52fcb63013c5c49e7436128c2dfaee31283","tid":106670,"uid":35578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T15:56:15.000Z","msg":"坐係入邊食飯唔會enjoy<br />\n熱帶雨林個感覺好似好污糟<br />\n仲好似隨時有蛇蟲鼠蟻係你隔離<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ab1c93304ede3e97fabeeccb962833b355fef26","tid":106670,"uid":54677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T17:16:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>嘢食太細個唔記得喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我淨係記得果時覺得水池條鱷魚好迫真，同埋棵大樹都好得人驚吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都覺得係，我仲記得啲人會掉錢落個池度<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n食食下野啲燈會突然暗左，跟住有啲動物吼叫聲，有啲猩猩會打心口，啲樹會猛咁搖，好似係<br />\n諗起都驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最後記得係啲野食好撚貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fdc6bccac3422bf179a04a30308779018c8337b","tid":106670,"uid":44289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T17:18:39.000Z","msg":"入面又有行雷閃電(effect)<br />\n仲有猩猩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成日畀啲雷聲嚇親<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家都24歲喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n諗返起其實呢間熱帶雨林餐廳其實好有特色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e937c5e77a09bae4d6b06f20ce4c9d1c428ebf21","tid":106670,"uid":28644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T17:19:30.000Z","msg":"次次入親去都喊到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仆街老豆仲要同我講話啲野係真"},{"pid":"721cdf4266da35ca684899317e86683e4faa17ac","tid":106670,"uid":65185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T17:21:44.000Z","msg":"98年果陣同表姐去過，記得兩個人一人一個餐（一大人一兒童餐）埋單2百幾$<br />\n照計都算高消費<br />\n<br />\nbtw ,間野係以前係又一城既邊個位置???"},{"pid":"bce5002251306ccc8016bf0d2d1e9923f69a527b","tid":106670,"uid":62755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T17:44:14.000Z","msg":"細個勁鍾意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc2fbec676c31203ec29a5444af753c9f1b4b0f1","tid":106670,"uid":42009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T17:47:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>98年果陣同表姐去過，記得兩個人一人一個餐（一大人一兒童餐）埋單2百幾$<br />\n照計都算高消費<br />\n<br />\nbtw ,間野係以前係又一城既邊個位置???</blockquote><br />\n最底層好似係！"},{"pid":"723240d8d348d781c4a8ee50b202fd9f8bd97b7e","tid":106670,"uid":42009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T17:48:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>入面又有行雷閃電(effect)<br />\n仲有猩猩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成日畀啲雷聲嚇親<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家都24歲喇<img src=\