 />\n係咁嫁咩？我記得入面好黑嫁喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我其實我冇去過未有IT之前既又一城<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  所以唔知係咪<br />\n純粹係外國食過呢間, 其實入面都偏暗架<br />\n<img src=\"http://e-lsi.com/libraries/images/portfolio/rainforest-cafe/rainforest-cafe-2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fe-lsi.com%2Flibraries%2Fimages%2Fportfolio%2Frainforest-cafe%2Frainforest-cafe-2.jpg&h=c627f3fa&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係諗呢間，唔黑唔恐怖喎！"}]}